Log::FileSimple README File
=====================================

A simple tool to write messages and objects dump to log file.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   FileHandle
   Data::Dumper

